featured_reviews.review_id: From the moment I walked in the staff were kind and open to questions. They have Tunnel of Love which is super fun and makes the experience light hearted. Their selection is MASSIVE and runs from cheap to very high quality. Most things have warranties on them which is great. Tanya and her training manager personally helped me with so many questions and great recommendations. They were so nice, knowledgeable and spent almost my whole time in there with me. My ONLY concern is they do take the products  out to look at if you want to see, and maybe I would suggest disposable gloves while handling products because you don't know who's touched it before and even though I clean everything, it's still kind of unsanitary in my opinion. I believe the prices were fair and at the end, because I spent $150 I got to spin a fun wheel for a free prize! Thank you for a great experience.

Secimleri MASIF'tir ve ucuzdan cok yuksek kaliteye kadar uzanir. Cogu seyin uzerinde garantileri var ki bu harika. Tanya ve egitim muduru, pek cok soru ve harika tavsiyelerle bana kisisel olarak yardimci oldu. Cok iyi, bilgili ve neredeyse butun zamanimi orada benimle gecirdiler. YALNIZCA endisem, urunleri gormek isterseniz bakmak icin cikariyorlar ve belki de urunleri tutarken tek kullanimlik eldivenler oneririm cunku daha once kimin dokundugunu bilmiyorsunuz ve her seyi temizlememe ragmen, yine de bir nevi. bence sagliksiz. Fiyatlarin adil olduguna inaniyorum ve sonunda 150 dolar harcadigim icin ucretsiz bir odul icin bir eglence carki cevirmem gerekti! Harika bir deneyim icin tesekkur ederiz.

featured_reviews.review_id: Not helpful at all. I had a 15% percent coupon, presented it. He put in, didn't think anything of it. Went home, after reviewing transaction, he only had taken off 5%. Since it had been more than "7 days" and because even though the receipt stated up to 90 days functional refund onto gift card, she stated she couldn't do anything since it was not "motorized" and she said that they are franchised and they don't have to honor what the customer service said when I had called them prior to coming into store. I told her I didn't want it, instead of offering other options, she pointed at the trash can outside in the front of the store. I don't recommend this store.

featured_reviews.review_id:
Start by saying the staff is great and always has been. I also like that the lights are nice and bright. There is a good variety of products.

Now the reason for giving 1 star.

This place is expensive and I cant spend these prices. Not all prices are over the top but a lot of them are. I also think it's time to update and clean the building as there is some water spots and holes in the ceiling and the products feel like we ar taking a trip in time to the early 2000's.

I would like to see the building cleaned up and made to feel more modern. Maybe cut some movies out to get a few more items in instead.

Personelin harika oldugunu ve her zaman oyle oldugunu soyleyerek baslayin. Isiklarin guzel ve parlak olmasini da seviyorum. Iyi bir urun cesitliligi var.

Simdi 1 yildiz vermemin nedeni.

Burasi pahali ve bu fiyatlari harcayamam. Fiyatlarin hepsi yuksek degil ama cogu oyle. Ayrica tavanda bazi su lekeleri ve delikler oldugundan ve urunler sanki 2000'li yillarin baslarina dogru bir zamanda yolculuk yapiyormusuz gibi hissettirdiginden, binayi guncelleme ve temizleme zamaninin geldigini dusunuyorum.

Binanin temizlendigini ve daha modern hissettirdigini gormek isterim. Belki bunun yerine birkac oge daha almak icin bazi filmleri kesebilirsiniz.
